Monte Carlo Method for Standardized Indirect Effect in a Simple Mediation Model Using SEM Assuming Multivariate Normal Distribution for Data Generated from a Multivariate Normal Distribution

Source: R/mcstdsem.R
mvn_std_mcmvnsem.Rd

Monte Carlo Method for Standardized Indirect Effect in a Simple Mediation Model Using SEM Assuming Multivariate Normal Distribution for Data Generated from a Multivariate Normal Distribution

mvn_std_mcmvnsem(data, taskid, R = 5000)

Arguments

data

n by 3 matrix or data frame. data[, 1] correspond to values for x. data[, 2] correspond to values for m. data[, 3] correspond to values for y.
taskid

Numeric. Task ID.
R

Integer. Monte Carlo replications.

See also

data <- mvn_dat(taskid = taskid)
mvn_std_mcmvnsem(data = data, taskid = taskid, R = 200)
